file: HookSubscriberRegistry.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Application\\Handler\\HookSubscriberRegistry"
type: final class
summary: The HookSubscriberRegistry maintains a registry of hook subscribers to facilitate event-driven dispatching within the application. It provides a lookup mechanism to retrieve specific subscribers associated with a given hook name.
